DescPackaging: <<
  Uses pkgconfig.
  Any package which BuildDepends on this one must also BuildDepend on:
    atk1 (>= 1.2.2-3), glib2-dev (>= 2.2.1-4), gtk+2-dev (>= 2.2.1-7), libxml2, pango1-dev (>= 1.2.1-4)

